---
title: Flujo de Estados CO (Solicitud de Credito)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: create() / status inicial

    pending --> fetching_bank_data: update_status()\nworkflow.on_enter -> fetching_bank_data_task
    fetching_bank_data --> validate_country_rules: fetching_bank_data_task\nupdate_status() success
    validate_country_rules --> approved: validate_country_rules_task\nupdate_status() valid=true
    validate_country_rules --> rejected: validate_country_rules_task\nupdate_status() valid=false

    pending --> technical_error: bootstrap error
    fetching_bank_data --> technical_error: retries agotados / fallo proveedor
    validate_country_rules --> technical_error: retries agotados / datos faltantes

    approved --> [*]
    rejected --> [*]
    technical_error --> [*]

    note right of pending
        CO conserva estado inicial pending.
        Despues usa pipeline simetrico con MX.
    end note

    note right of validate_country_rules
        Persiste CountryValidation antes
        de transicionar a estado terminal.
    end note
